{
  "stem": "1183.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the train had to stop because of engine trouble.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the meantime, they bombarded the train station in Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, we were-- we could travel further and it was all February, March 1945.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were also-- and then at that time, we were in open cattle wagons and it was freezing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were standing the night in front of the camp of Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember they wanted to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they asked, like in a hotel, we want those people in there, those women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Bergen-Belsen they-- it was too full, packed, no accommodation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they had to carry us further.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we went to-- [INAUDIBLE] several names-- and then we went to last one was-- not the last one-- one of the last ones was Porta Westfalica.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was-- as I remember, we had appell outside in a-- in a green grassy area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You saw the nature.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember when-- once when we were on appell, there was people there on the mountain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were filming us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Germans saw that, and they put the dogs and-- up to the people, you know, to see what was-- because we were a ragged bunch, naturally, at that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They tried to put us to work in the caves, because originally there was a Telefunken and there was equipment there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, the machines were there, but equipment was not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was I think the end of March, beginning of April.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sat there and didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You come a little bit too rest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long we were there, no idea of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then from Porta Westfalica we probably went to another one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
